  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Problem: SafeERC20 calls callOptionalReturn which uses .call(..) without .gas(..) which passes all the gas to the call and allows called contract to drain all used gas and perform GasToken minting https://medium.com/level-k/public-disclosure-malicious-gastoken-minting-236b2f8ace38\r\n\r\nRecommendation: allow the caller of SafeERC20 to limit the gas used by adding additional parameter to the functions. This parameter will also make those who use SafeERC20 aware of the possible gas drain.",
